text: Dagsin is a 2016 Filipino drama film directed by Atom Magadia. It was shortlisted as a potential entry by the Philippines for the Best International Feature Film at the 92nd Academy Awards. ==Cast== * Tommy Abuel as Justino * Lotlot De Leon as Mercy * Benjamin Alves as Young Justino * Janine Gutierrez as Young Corazon * Sue Prado as Grace ==References== ==External links== * Category:2016 films Category:2016 drama films Category:Philippine films Category:Philippine drama films Category:Filipino-language films Category:Tagalog-language films
